title: High Educational Attainment
description: In 2022, 61.1% of Montenegro's population aged 25 and over had attained at least a Bachelor's degree, with 65.5% of males and 58.2% of females achieving this level of education.

title: Low Measles Immunization Rate
description: In 2023, only 24% of children aged 12-23 months in Montenegro were immunized against measles, indicating a low vaccination coverage.
